Read the CRM-style activity log for a lead (calls, emails, meetings — actions performed by humans or prior agent runs). Paginated (`count` 1-200 default 20, `page` 0-indexed).

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} before contacting the lead, to avoid duplicating outreach the team already did.

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} when the lead summary's `prospecting_actions_count` is 0.
